jira - Jira CLI

USAGE:
    jira <action> [options...]

DESCRIPTION:
    Jira command-line interface for various Jira operations.

ARGUMENTS:
    action
        Jira action to perform (required)

    options...
        Action-specific options

EXAMPLES:
    jira list
    jira create --type=Bug --summary="Issue title"
    jira transition ISSUE-123 --to="In Progress"
